         <abstract id="aspace_e2ddd2aa9cbc9890a962f943fec4e6a1">The materials consist of diplomae examinatorium of Yale College. The diplomae were read at commencement and include a formal greeting from the president of the college and a list of candidates for degrees. The diplomae are written in Latin and signed by the president.</abstract>
    
      </did>
